the Ju&s;tices of the Peace for the time being, for the &s;everal re&s;pecti<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> Counties afore&s;aid, for which they &s;hall be Ju&s;tices of the Peace, do with<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> fourty days after the publication hereof, a&s;&s;emble and meet togeth<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> in the Court Hou&s;es for the &s;everal and re&s;pecti<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> City's and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> or &s;uch other place or places as they &s;hall agree on, and there order <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> the A&s;&s;e&s;&s;ors and Collectors for the City's of <HI>New-York</HI> and <HI>Albany</HI>&punc; <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> the &s;everal and re&s;pective Towns Mannors or Liberties within their <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Juri&s;dictions, for the A&s;&s;e&s;&s;ing Collecting and receiving of the pu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">li<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> Rates, for the defraying the publick Charge of each re&s;pective City's <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Counties afore&s;aid, be the A&s;&s;e&s;&s;ors &amp; Collectors for the a&s;&s;e&s;&s;ing collectin<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> and Receiving the Sum and Sums of Money herein before mentioned&punc; a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">cording to the proportions before expre&s;&s;ed, as to the &s;aid Mayor Alderm<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> and Ju&s;tices &s;hall &s;eem meet and rea&s;onable, and for as much as there <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> &s;everal Towns Mannors and Juri&s;dictions within the re&s;pective County afore&s;aid, who refu&s;e neglect or do not elect annually or once ev<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ry <